 * Create the OSSIM database using the wwwconfig-common package

   Create an ossim database user?
    . /usr/share/wwwconfig-common/mysql-createuser.sh
   Insert mysql tables?
    . /usr/share/wwwconfig-common/mysql-createdb.sh

